data.description: Motivated Seller!!! This one year old 3 Bedroom/2 Bath home is located in a convenient location. Built in 2022 this home is like new with an open floor plan, stainless appliances, custom cabinets, plank flooring, walk in closets, and double vanities in the master bathroom. Outside on the 0.74 acre lot the home has an asphalt driveway, wood privacy fence surrounding the backyard, extended 12 x24 wood deck, and 12x24 storage building.
